metadata.description:
... The human being

Wood and other materials offer different possibilities to describe the human being in its particularity.

Through form and material, vulnerability but also hardness and coldness can be expressed. As an artist, I have taken up this theme and depicted different characters and their traits in these materials.

All images in this collection are 2560 x 3840 resolution.

Original art by man2art.

Created with :
Chainsaw - Canon EOS - Illustrator - Photoshop
